    "description": "A comprehensive Postman collection for Stripe's payment services API, covering key endpoints for Payments, Billing, and more. All requests use the base URL https://api.stripe.com/v1/, require a secret API key (obtain from Stripe Dashboard, e.g., sk_test_...), and use form-encoded request bodies with JSON responses. Supports test mode for safe testing. Covers all major resources as of August 2025, based on official documentation and Stripe's Postman collection.",
